<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #333;">OTP Verification</h1>
        <p>Dear user,</p>
        <p>Here is your one-time password (OTP) for verification:</p>
        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px;">
            {{otp}}
        </div>
        <p>This code will expire in 5 minutes. Please use it to verify your account.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this verification code, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The FX Trading Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
